Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.01,OP6,,0,0,0,,OP Start
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:16.00,OP6,,0,0,0,,Hey boys, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:20.60,OP6,,0,0,0,,Humans aren't such a big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:25.44,OP6,,0,0,0,,Who needs tomorrow anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:28.71,OP6,,0,0,0,,so don't hide your fists
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:32.92,OP6,,0,0,0,,You're not old enough
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:39.29,OP6,,0,0,0,,to sell your dreams away to uncertainty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.23,0:00:44.66,OP6,,0,0,0,,Hey boys, you're the only ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.66,0:00:48.26,OP6,,0,0,0,,who can pull the trigger in your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:51.64,OP6,,0,0,0,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.64,0:00:54.64,OP6,,0,0,0,,We're living in this senseless, ridiculous,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:59.01,OP6,,0,0,0,,awesome world right at this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:01.48,OP6,,0,0,0,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:07.35,OP6,,0,0,0,,Don't forget every truth or lie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:11.08,OP6,,0,0,0,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,0:01:13.42,OP6,,0,0,0,,We're way too young to die
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:18.29,OP6,,0,0,0,,In this empty town lined with empty faces
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.29,0:01:20.56,OP6,,0,0,0,,All the kids took off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:23.10,OP6,,0,0,0,,into this windless night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.10,0:01:29.00,OP6,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,3000)}Because they want to change something
Comment: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:31.07,OP6,,0,0,0,,OP End
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.03,0:01:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with... this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.77,0:02:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the best you've got...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is all you've got,\NI still don't need to use that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't realized it?\NI... haven't used my Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mock me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have enough strength\Nor desire...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:03:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you are weak?\NBecause you don't have enough... hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If I kept playing comrade with you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have... been able to get...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,... this much power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right... I need...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.13,0:03:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Both power... and hatred...\Nin order to catch up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:50.04,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\blur4\fad(600,0)\pos(662,550)\3c&H000000&}Itachi and Sasuke\NToo Far Away
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother... I'll get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:03:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place...\Nwhere Father works, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... The headquarters\Nof the Leaf Police Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was curious about it from before,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but why's the Uchiha Clan crest\Non the Police Force mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... so you noticed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Let me see...\NTo put it simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems the previous generations\Nof the Uchiha Clan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,set up and established the Police Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So they used their own crest for\Nthe symbol mark of this organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,From olden times,\Nthe Uchiha Clan has always been
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in charge of protecting\Nthe public and the peace of this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Uchiha crest is\Na testament to the proud clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The Uchiha Clan has gotten small now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But even now, nearly all members\Nbelong to this first force here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and contribute to maintaining\Npeace in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Only even more exceptional Shinobi\Ncan crack down on the crimes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,committed by Shinobi, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, father's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to enter\Nthe Police Force, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Leaf Police Force
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When I grow up, I'm also going\Nto enter the Police Force, so!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Father's also coming to\Ntomorrow's entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first step to my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late... What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to talk to you about.\NCome quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:06:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come this far just half a year\Nafter being promoted to Chunin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,About tomorrow's special mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided to go with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you complete this mission, Itachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,your entrance into\Nthe Anbu Black Ops is almost assured!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be so worried.\NMore importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's mission will be\Na very important mission not just for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but for the Uchiha Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quitting tomorrow's mission, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing talking insanity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know how important\Na day tomorrow is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to Sasuke's Academy\Nentrance ceremony tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The general rule is for relatives\Nto attend the Academy entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There was the notice, right... Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the Academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your left leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to ice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother... He's so distant...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Congratulations\Non your entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on, please work very hard\Ntowards striving for the Shinobi path.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd like you to bring further prosperity\Nto the Hidden Village in the Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee... I remember\Nthe time when Itachi entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what I'd expect from his brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your help with both boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The first prodigy since the beginning\Nof the Academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There were no students\Nas exceptional as that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a bit too much praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hopeful for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Become a fine Shinobi\Nlike your big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... That's Uchiha, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder... if he's awesome, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Recess at last! What a drag.\NI'm still not used to this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You want some too, Shikamaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, all of your recesses\Nhave become meal times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've great confidence\Nyou'll make it great in Anbu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a long way... to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:10:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You should rest your body\Non your days off at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to push it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard... that Big Brother graduated\Nfrom the Academy in just one year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The times are different, then and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, that kid is a bit special, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'm going to hand out\Nthe report cards for the first half.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Taijutsu: 1st in class and academy\NNinjutsu: 1st in class and academy\NIndividual rank: 1st in class and academy\NTeam rank: 1st in class and academy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do a fine job in this vein like\Nyour big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Father... I wanted you to say,\N"That's my boy," to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean you can't participate\Nin the assembly tomorrow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand your own position!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm setting out on a mission tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What're they doing this late\Nat night with the lights off?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What mission?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say...\NIt's a top secret mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi... You also have the role\Nof the pipe which connects the clan
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,with the keystone of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep that well in mind!\NAnd come to tomorrow's assembly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.68,0:12:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to bed after\Nyou've gone to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing hanging around\Nthis late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.28,0:12:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Report Card
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Father only thinks about you, Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I loathsome to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's logical for Shinobi to be\Nill-thought of by people, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not how I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother's right.\NI really do... think ill of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellence is not easy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have power,\Nyou become alienated and also arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're coveted\Nand sought after at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But, we only have each other\Nfor siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I will continue to exist with you\Nas a wall you must get over...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm ill-thought of...\NThat's what a big brother is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Itachi home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to\Ntalk to you about. Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's everyone gathered here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two people who didn't come\Nto yesterday's assembly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't go to the assembly Father\Nwas talking about last night, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that when you enter Anbu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you get roped into various\Ntroublesome things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father also said something\Nlike that in your defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But for us, we don't intend\Nto treat you special.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:14:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. I shall be careful next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm going to have\Nto ask you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... But before that,\Nthere's a little more I want to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about Uchiha Shisui who threw himself\Ninto the Nakano River to kill himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Threw himself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The other person who didn't come\Nto the assembly is that Shisui.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,As I recall, you adored him\Nlike a real older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... I hadn't seen him at all recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And we the Police Force have decided\Nto launch an all-out investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Investigation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the will Shisui wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The analysis of the handwriting\Nhas been completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No mistake, he did indeed write it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If there are no murder leads,\Nthen what's the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be easy for a person who can use\NSharingan to copy handwriting, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The most adept Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The man feared as Shisui,\N"the lnstantaneous Man."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a man who would take\Nthe lead no matter what the mission
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,if it was for the sake of the clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tough to think that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,such a man would leave something\Nlike this and kill himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't judge people...\Nonly on looks and speculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,For the time being,\NI leave the will with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that and you request cooperation\Nin the investigation from Anbu Black Ops.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we get a lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, we have a different route\Nto Anbu Black Ops.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll know right away if you do something\Nlike crushing the investigation request.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just come right out\Nand say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You suspect me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's right, you little punk...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try doing something\Nlike betraying the clan and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll cost you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't judge people...\Nonly on looks and speculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you take the liberty to\Njudge me as patient and take me lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Clan... Clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You measure incorrectly\Nthe size of your own vessels
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and don't know the depth of mine,\Nso you grovel there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen him like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shisui... was monitoring you recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Half a year after entering Anbu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the strangeness of your behavior\Ncouldn't be overlooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fixated on the organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,fixated on the clan,\Nfixated on the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dreadful thing that constrains oneself\Nand labels one's own vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a foolish thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that fear and hate...\Nwhat one has never seen or known...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Itachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell's the matter\Nwith you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi...\NYou've been a little strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not strange at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm carrying out my own role...\NThat's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why didn't you come last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to elevate myself higher...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My vessel is dismayed\Nat this foolish clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,From olden times,\Nthe Uchiha Clan has all along
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,been in charge protecting\Nthe peace of this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Uchiha crest is a testament\Nto the proud clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've great confidence\Nyou'll do great in Anbu Black Ops.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're fixated\Non insignificant things like clans...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you lose sight of what's truly important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,T rue change cannot be made if stuck\Nwithin the restrictions of regulations,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and constrained predictions\Nand imagination...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying such arrogant things!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! You'll be imprisoned\Nif you say any more foolish nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellence is not easy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have power,\Nyou become alienated and also arrogant...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:19:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,even if you're coveted\Nand sought after at first...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... Big Brother...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tolerate it anymore...\NCaptain, order im prisonment!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother! Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the one who killed Shisui.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I apologize for\Nmy numerous slips of the tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.38,0:19:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently, it seems he's been up\Nto his ears in Anbu Black Ops missions
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and was a little tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Anbu Black Ops is a force\Nunder the direct control of Lord Hokage...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even we the Police Force can't arrest him,\Nif we don't have an arrest warrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And as for Itachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take the responsibility\Nand monitor him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, you've woken up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a hindrance back at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But it won't be like that this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you...\Nthe true power of Sharingan.
Comment: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:07.78,ED9,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.24,0:21:18.07,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}When I recalled the parts one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:24.44,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}I felt as though I had understood everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:35.01,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Faded words which I kept so close to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:44.79,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Speechless nights, a hint of warmth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:51.53,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}and this distant yearning for you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:22:00.84,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}I live, simply repeating this cycle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.02,0:22:12.55,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Held in my two hands is a droplet of time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:23.00,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Softly clutching forgotten memories, lost words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:36.80,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}{\fad(0,2500)}I'll keep these thoughts...
Comment: 0,0:22:37.74,0:22:37.80,ED9,,0,0,0,,ED End
